<ul><li><b>Scattering</b>&nbsp;of the beam of electrons by the nuclei occurs&nbsp;<b>due to their charge</b>. This causes the <b>intensity to decrease</b>&nbsp;as angle&nbsp;\(\theta\)&nbsp;increases.<br></li><li><b>Diffraction</b>&nbsp;of the beam of electrons by each nuclei causes&nbsp;<b>intensity maxima and minima</b>&nbsp;to be superimposed on the scattering pattern.<br></li></ul>